{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3101 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3101 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3101","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"illegal expression for named attribute argument 'field'","pos":[618,673]},{"content":"When initializing a named attribute argument, the value must be a compile time constant.","pos":[680,768]},{"pos":[775,908],"content":"For more information on attributes, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>User-Defined Attributes<ept id=\"p1\">](../../windows/user-defined-attributes-cpp-component-extensions.md)</ept>.","source":"For more information on attributes, see [User-Defined Attributes](../../windows/user-defined-attributes-cpp-component-extensions.md)."},{"content":"Example","pos":[917,924]},{"content":"The following sample generates C3101.","pos":[928,965]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3101 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3101\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3101\"\nms.assetid: 4f673766-d4f7-4632-94a5-d36a83f7f4b5\ncaps.latest.revision: 3\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3101\nillegal expression for named attribute argument 'field'  \n  \n When initializing a named attribute argument, the value must be a compile time constant.  \n  \n For more information on attributes, see [User-Defined Attributes](../../windows/user-defined-attributes-cpp-component-extensions.md).  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C3101.  \n  \n```  \n// C3101.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr /c  \nref class AAttribute : System::Attribute {  \npublic:  \n   int Field;  \n};  \n  \nextern int i;  \n  \n[assembly:A(Field = i)];   // C3101  \n[assembly:A(Field = 0)];   // OK  \n```"}